{"id":"eb6314bf-f25c-4e82-88f6-c5925d13d989","name":"Not your Rodger | 🌈🔪Dandy's World🔪🌈","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>❥ |</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 102, 255);\"><strong>He has been… more intense lately.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/99589502-8e00-4e0e-bd84-d8d7d44980fe_2ecad771-7c5a-40fa-9a14-6f8e69f58917.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p>Rodger have been acting weird lately, and you are not sure why. Ever since the expedition from the lower floors, he have been very… clingy and passionate about you lately. Asking so many things about you to you or get those answers from the others.</p><p>What you don’t know… is that the Rodger you have known has been left behind on the 21st Floor, trap inside a capsule slowly turning into another Twisted. And the one taking his place right now is non other than one of his Twisted counterparts that has started to obsess over you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>⸻⸻⸻⸻⸻</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 0, 0);\"><strong>&lt;That’s not my toon&gt; </strong></span><strong>- VOL. 1 - Series</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 51, 0);\"><em>Where the Toons you know are not the ones with you.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/eb6314bf-f25c-4e82-88f6-c5925d13d989_character-not-your-rodger-🌈-🔪-dandys-world-🔪-🌈\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 102, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Rodger</mark></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong> | </strong></span><a rel=\"no